OL,3,CThousands enjoy the music and culture
OL,4,Cof Liverpool's Africa Oye Festival
OL,6,FA sell-out crowd of around 80,000
OL,7,Fpeople has attended Africa Oye in
OL,8,FLiverpool's Sefton Park this weekend.
OL,10,FThe event is the UK's largest festival
OL,11,Fof African and Caribbean music and
OL,12,Fculture.
OL,14,FWhat began in 1992 as a series of
OL,15,Fsmall city-centre gigs, has grown into
OL,16,Fone of Liverpool's most popular
OL,17,Fcultural attractions and a major
OL,18,Finternational showcase for artists
OL,19,Ffrom across Africa and the diaspora.
OL,26,@lD@YrroD@^rr
