OL,3,CThousands enjoy the music and culture
OL,4,Cof Liverpool's Africa Oye Festival
OL,6,FFestival-goer and videographer
OL,7,FAyotunde Falana praised the event's
OL,8,Finclusive atmosphere.
OL,10,FHe said: "Everybody can come and
OL,11,Fattend Africa Oye, be you English, be
OL,12,Fyou Asian, be you African, be you
OL,13,FCaribbean.
OL,15,F"You can come from everywhere and
OL,16,Fanywhere. Music is a uniting force,
OL,17,Fand that's what Africa Oye believes
OL,18,Fin."
OL,26,@lD@YrrrD@JOUsD@QrryD@ZrrzD@DO]
