OL,3,CThousands enjoy the music and culture
OL,4,Cof Liverpool's Africa Oye Festival
OL,6,FAmong the performers was Senegalese
OL,7,Fsinger-songwriter Oumy, who said the
OL,8,Ffestival provided an important
OL,9,Fplatform for African artists.
OL,11,F"It means a lot and I'm really happy
OL,12,Fto be the artist to represent
OL,13,FSenegal," she said.
OL,26,@lD@YrrsD@AOUuD@IO]
