OL,3,CThousands enjoy the music and culture
OL,4,Cof Liverpool's Africa Oye Festival
OL,6,FAfrica Oye Artistic Director Paul
OL,7,FDuhaney highlighted the diversity of
OL,8,Fthe audience. "You see every
OL,9,Fdemographic you can think of from
OL,10,Fethnicity to social background and
OL,11,Fage," he said. "We're showcasing the
OL,12,Fbest of this nation in one park and
OL,13,Fit's beautiful to see."
OL,15,FThe festival returned this year as a
OL,16,Fticketed event for the first time in
OL,17,Fits history, while continuing its long-
OL,18,Fstanding mission of promoting
OL,19,Fmulticulturalism, understanding and
OL,20,Ftolerance.
OL,26,@lD@YrrnD@JrrpD@OOUsD@EO]sD@POUuD@WO]
